<title>CANADA: Veritas DGC markets share offering.</title>
<headline>Veritas DGC markets share offering.</headline>
<dateline>CALGARY 1997-07-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Veritas DGC Inc said on Thursday that it marketed its public offering of three million common shares at US$23.50 a share.</p>
<p>The company said the expected US$67 million in proceeds from the sale would be used for general corporate purposes.</p>
<p>((Paul Simao, Reuters Toronto Bureau (416) 941-8104))</p>
